==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sizing
<hw>Siz"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Act of covering or
treating with size.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A weak glue used in various trades; size.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sizing</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sizing
<hw>Siz"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of sorting with
respect to size.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act of bringing anything to a certain
size.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Univ. of Cambridge, Eng.)</fld> <def>Food and drink
ordered from the buttery by a student.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sizy</ent>⟦br⟧
